title: #92Noon! Boudreau/RJ/Leber/Russo/Terrill
description: Wild HC Bruce Boudreau opens the show, followed by Vikings A-Topics and Ron Johnson to wrap the final hour. Leber in studio midway through, with Russo calling in after news. Super Bowl Stories with Craig Terrill('05 Seahawks) to close!
